I want to get Ads Invoice

To get your Ads Invoice, you can go to the 'Billing' tab in your NewsBreak account. There, you'll find the 'Transaction History' section where you can review and download your invoices. If you need further assistance, feel free to reach out!

If you're having trouble finding the 'Transaction History' in your NewsBreak account, make sure you're logged in and navigate to the 'Billing' tab. It should be located there. If it's still not visible, please check if there are any updates or changes to the interface. If you continue to have issues, you might want to contact support at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance.
